title: GET_INTERIOR_GROUP_ID
content:
0xE4A84ABF135EF91A0x09D6376F// GetInteriorGroupId
int GET_INTERIOR_GROUP_ID(int interior);Returns the group ID of the specified interior. For example, regular interiors have group 0, subway interiors have group 1. There are a few other groups too.
codeBlocks: Returns the group ID of the specified interior. For example, regular interiors have group 0, subway interiors have group 1. There are a few other groups too.
